item.title: Project 2: BSE Closure Anomaly Detection
item.description: Detect Outliers in the BSE Index Data 1991-2019 Build an LSTM Autoencoder in Keras Detect anomalies with Autoencoders in time series data Interactive charts and plots using Plotly Python and Seaborn for data visualization. Link to Github Repository

item.title: Project 1: Learn Two Digit Numbers
item.description: Create a web application to draw a two-digit number and learn what it is. Train the model locally on the browser. To optimize the pretraining time data is loaded in the form of Sprite Sheet. Visualization of model training is done using tfvis.show() TensorFlow function. CNN model is trained on the MNIST dataset. Link to Github Repository
